msgid ""
"The third material necessary for improved buildings is thatch reed, used to\n"
"cover roofs. Thatch reed is planted by a ferner around his building, the\n"
"fernery."
msgstr ""
"Tretím materiálom, ktorý je potrebný pre vylepšené budovy, je trstina,\n"
"ktorá sa používa na pokrývanie striech. Sadí ju trstinár okolo svojej "
"budovy,\n"
"trstinovej farmy."

